Package: qrb-audio-manager
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: QRB Audio Manager Library
 It creates stream based on client requests (PlaybackStream for playback,
 RecordThread for record), provides operations on the stream, and maintains
 its lifecycle.
